FBIS3-18522 "drweu043_h_94009" FBIS-WEU-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 GERMANY Union, Employers To Meet LD0303154094 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 1516 GMT 3 Mar 94 LD0303154094 Berlin DDP/ADN Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Cologne (DDP/ADN) -- IG Metall and the metalworkers employers have agreed to top level talks on 4 March concerning the pay dispute in the west German metal industry, according to Gesamtmetall [employers' organization]. DDP/ADN learned this from Dieter Kirchner, the main business manager of Gesamtmetall, in Cologne on 3 March. The meeting will take place in Hanover, late in the afternoon of 4 March.
